{"tid":820231,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同齡既女開始嫁人，自己就一條女都未溝過","createTime":"2018-09-15T09:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T11:12:03.000Z","uid":58316,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"37b81de06ccfe2c5566cc02578481d0e1b105db0","tid":820231,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:59:08.000Z","msg":"好記得<br />\nf3某週末搭巴士返屋企<br />\n咁呢程車係途經好多學校<br />\n自己個間<br />\n同某女校<br />\n個陣仲係熱狗<br />\n架車又嘈<br />\n就咁坐都成頭汗<br />\n去到學校<br />\n有兩條友上車<br />\n原來係同班<br />\n另一個係條女<br />\n我都識<br />\n唔知朗誦定咩識<br />\n但真係想像唔到佢地一齊<br />\n心諗佢地一個游水踢波<br />\n一個朗誦拉琴<br />\n到而家都唔知佢地點識<br />\nanyway<br />\n一上架車<br />\n可能因為我坐打側個行<br />\n見我唔到<br />\n坐係落車門前個兩人位<br />\n搭搭下<br />\n個女就成個頭訓落男仔大脾度<br />\n我同學係咁掃佢頭髮<br />\n（條女頭髮好靚，親眼見過幾次）<br />\n睇唔到佢表情<br />\n但心諗一定好撚冧啦冚家剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住就係女校落車<br />\n<br />\n當年d女<br />\n而家開始嫁人<br />\n不過以我所知冇一個生仔<br />\n反而有d男同學<br />\n太子爺個d<br />\n大學未讀完就奉子成婚<br />\n而我<br />\n到今時今日<br />\n一路走來<br />\n仲未同過一個女人講我愛你<br />\n仲未錫過女人一啖"},{"pid":"8144c38c3e63f6c2ff153cea2a132e8b1ab97cf0","tid":820231,"uid":194687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T10:01:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a142b6ad23c651b75fe6c1c92e35bc19cd6aa05","tid":820231,"uid":190714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T10:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17698daf13f0d0e653dd6a7cc92a6b820a369d09","tid":820231,"uid":187108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T10:03:49.000Z","msg":"不要再說了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edeac9427eda85750b30d2daf302131b297c62a7","tid":820231,"uid":34241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T10:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9f55cac2f489287857ab64e975474774f32181","tid":820231,"uid":23218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T10:16:49.000Z","msg":"比個機會你同我講我愛你"},{"pid":"60bbf713bb075c3985cd63d9275a0aa447940e49","tid":820231,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T10:19:42.000Z","msg":"唔好再講呀😡😞😭"},{"pid":"64fda45ff8c5798d6d712f784874e8cc008c3a58","tid":820231,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T10:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12f54a0d5a81e9fdcda5289f1f11b692863eebf","tid":820231,"uid":60787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T10:23:45.000Z","msg":"為何無人愛我<br />\n夜夜獨自一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2fa67b55af1bc1078b92a74c0f511eace4d304d","tid":820231,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T10:26:33.000Z","msg":"愛係窮人發明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92533f18d06e5a47383a8d7a2f6b930e8b892540","tid":820231,"uid":198165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T11:10:01.000Z","msg":"你搵人起我底？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1391ae27ed36b556d172c27827795ca250d9ebd","tid":820231,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T11:12:03.000Z","msg":"窮撚有咩好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}